title: Origins of Reid Fleming, World's Toughest Milkman (1998) David B
description:
This collects the earliest adventures of the two-fisted milkman, strips that originally appeared in Canadas Georgia Straight and Vancouver Free Press newspapers in 1978-79. Also includes the first Reid Fleming strip, previously unpublished, as well as essays by Boswell about the history of the character and the strip. Story, art and cover by David Boswell.
